<b>What's new:</b>
<p>
<ul>
<li>replace penguin with bear
<li>change "Sea-level temperature" to "Sea-level air temperature" on climate control
<li>change "temperature" to "air temperature" on graphs
<li>update equilibrium line if climate is changed while clock is paused
<li>remove Restart clock button, semantics don't make sense for this sim
<li>fix algorithm for ELA ice surface intersection, it was broken close to terminus
</ul>
<p>
<b>Known problems:</b>
<ul>
<li>none
</ul>
<p>
<b>Not implemented:</b>
<ul>
<li>snowfall is not visible
<li>can't switch between English and metric units
<li>time-based graphs are not implemented
<li>"Steady State" button doesn't advance clock time
<li>features need to be split into Intro, Advanced, and Climate Experiments panels
<li>interface for climate experiments is not implemented
</ul>
